title: Swing-N-Slide WS 5110 Two Extreme Duty Yellow Swing Seats with a Stand-Up Swing Swing Set Refresher Bundle, Yellow
features: Includes a two heavy duty yellow swing seats with chains and a stand up swing
Each swing seat measures 26" X 6" X . 5" And features heavy-duty reinforced plastic seat attached to plastic coated steel chain with pelican hooks

description: Upgrade your 3 position swing beam swing set with this refresher bundle by Swing-N-Slide. This exciting bundle features two Yellow extreme duty swing seats and a stand-up swing, all with pinch-free coated chains. Each heavy duty swing supports up to 250 pounds when attached to a heavy duty swing hanger (not included), allowing parents to swing alongside their children. The Stand-Up swing supports up to 115 pounds and provides a unique swinging experience that utilize full body movement to gain momentum and speed. All three swings feature coated chains for a pinch-free and secure grip and can be adjusted for variable Height. Each swing seat measure 26" X 6" In a heavy duty reinforced plastic design while the Stand-Up swing base measure 14" X 14". This bundle is perfect for the entire family; upgrade or refresh your swing set today!
